title: Didn't received a single thing Ten-year gifts,
body:
I've been play this game for years and i Didn't receive the icon gift.
Why?

replies.body: There are a lot of accounts to cover, so it's going to take some time for the process to wrap up.  We have updated provided through our [support ticker](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Let me know if you have any questions!
The gifts are still being distributed. The 23rd is the final day, so if you don't receive anything by then, you can submit a support ticket.
